SQLQuery.Name: SQL Query 1
SQLQuery.SQLQueryExpression:
select a.*, case when a."TIMELY" = 'Yes' and a."DISPUTE" != 'Yes' and a."SUB_ISSUE" is null then 'good' else 'bad' end
bank_level, case when a."CRIME_RATES" > 500 then 'very high' when a."CRIME_RATES" <= 500 and a."CRIME_RATES" > 400 then 'high' when a."CRIME_RATES" <= 400 and a."CRIME_RATES" > 300 then 'normal' when a."CRIME_RATES" <= 300 and a."CRIME_RATES" > 200 then 'low' when a."CRIME_RATES" <= 200 then 'very low'
end crime_cal from "Join_N$10009" a
